Chordate:



Chordate stopped outside of the conference room Feline had said.  He wondered 
what was so slagging important he had to miss something as fun as a walk with 
the beautiful kitty next to him.  He looked over to her, smiling, gently 
taking his hand away from hers.  "Ready?"
